v = RC.map cell ++ [RB]

From the first equation: [LB] ++ LC.map cell ends with leftBound. But LC.map cell consists of cell symbols (not leftBound). So LC must be empty and [LB] = u ++ [leftBound], giving u = [].

With LC = []: LC.reverse = [].

